comment:
{"1": {"comment_id": "its_five_oclock_somewhereuk"  "comment_text": "It’s a little after 5pm in São Paulo  Brazil 🇧🇷
I don’t know what it’s been like where you are  but we’ve had a glorious  sunny day here!
And when it’s sunny  it’s hard not to crave sitting in the sun with fabulously summery cocktail!
Now  I’ve always loved a mojito. And I’ve not whipped one up for a while. So todays wonderful weather was all the inspiration I needed!!

Watermelon Mojito

35ml @bacardi
35ml @palmbeachliqueurs watermelon rum liqueur
35ml simple syrup
6 chunks of fresh watermelon
A handful of fresh mint
One fresh lime (cut into small wedges)
@doubledutchdrinks watermelon soda (to top up)

Muddle the lime  simple syrup  melon and mint in the bottom of your glass. Half fill@with crushed ice and give it all a good stir. Add the watermelon rum and the bacardi and give it another good stir. Fill the glass with crushed ice and top up with the watermelon soda.
I garnished with a sprig of fresh mint and a large slice of fresh watermelon!

It’s summertime!!

Cheers 🥂

main_text: La Boum5 cl Cachaça3 cl Fresh lime juice2 cl Sugar syrup5 cl Fresh watermelon juice1 Dash of Pimento BittersPut all ingredients together in a shaker and shake vigorously with crushed ice. Pour into a tumbler without straining and top up with more crushed ice if necessary. Garnish with mint. Enjoy.As some might know we are not always the best at jumping on the hypetrain but we only regret it sometimes. In this case we do. When @swetlanaholz  bar manager at Hamburg's @barlelion  went viral in the summer of 2021 with her La Boum cocktail - a kind of watermelon caipirinha - we really wanted to remix the drink. But we were so sluggish that various underage flatmates consistently munched away any melon we acquired before we could sacrifice it to the juicer.Now in 2022 we finally caught up with La Boum when it fought its way back into social media attention and onto various German bar menus along with the first rays of sunshine. And yes we missed out on a real awesome drink last year - fruity fresh light quaffable with a pretty new taste thanks to watermelon which is played far too seldom. And it’s such a nice drink to look at also. Yeah we should have listened to practically everyone else last year. Sorry.#laboumcocktail #laboum #watermelon #watermeloncocktail #cachaca #cachaça #mixology #thirsty #drinkstagram #cocktailsofinstagram #cocktailhour #cocktailtime #imbibe #cocktailoftheday #homebar #imbibegram #drinksofinstagram #howisummer #homebartender #liqpic #cocktailsathome
comment:
{"1": {"comment_id": "therealcocktailbart"  "comment_text": "La Boum

5 cl Cachaça
3 cl Fresh lime juice
2 cl Sugar syrup
5 cl Fresh watermelon juice
1 Dash of Pimento Bitters

Put all ingredients together in a shaker and shake vigorously with crushed ice. Pour into a tumbler without straining and top up with more crushed ice if necessary. Garnish with mint. Enjoy.

As some might know  we are not always the best at jumping on the hypetrain  but we only regret it sometimes. In this case  we do. When @swetlanaholz   bar manager at Hamburg's @barlelion   went viral in the summer of 2021 with her La Boum cocktail - a kind of watermelon caipirinha - we really wanted to remix the drink. But we were so sluggish that various underage flatmates consistently munched away any melon we acquired  before we could sacrifice it to the juicer.

Now  in 2022  we finally caught up with La Boum when it fought its way back into social media attention and onto various German bar menus along with the first rays of sunshine. And yes  we missed out on a real awesome drink last year - fruity  fresh  light  quaffable  with a pretty new taste thanks to watermelon  which is played far too seldom. And it’s such a nice drink to look at  also. Yeah  we should have listened to practically everyone else last year. Sorry.

main_text: The Mango called the “king of fruits” is the most widely consumed fruit in the world. Native to India and Southeast Asia where it has been cultivated for over 5000 years mango delivers on all levels. In addition to the juicy tropical flavour mango is an excellent source of vitamin C Vitamin A vitamin B6 folates and fibre. Mango not only contributes valuable nutrients it classified as a low glycaemic food which can be helpful for managing blood sugar levels.On the other hand; Watermelon as the name suggests is around 90% water which makes it useful for staying hydrated in the summer. Watermelon is native to Africa and has been cultivated since ancient times. It is a good source of vitamin C and contains decent amounts of potassium copper vitamin B5 and vitamin A. Sipping on watermelon juice after sweating is known to be beneficial too. Doing so helps prevent muscle soreness as long as you don't push yourself too hard.Did you know Mango belongs to the Cashew family and also that every part of the watermelon can be consumed including seeds and rind?...#befit_india #fitness #training #healthylifestyle #watermelon #citrus #healthyfood #fruitlover #cucumber #Hydration #Water #DrinkWater #Diet #Nutrition #HealthyEating #mango #watermelon #melons #watermelons #wellness #fruit #fruits #instafood #summer #healthyfood #delicious #vegan #foodblogger #healthy #mangoes

main_text: BE YOUR OWN REASON TO SMILE.😄The mandatory summer post. 🌞🍉Red colour of this amazing summer fruit comes from lycopene an antioxidant which protects from sun burn. Lycopene may help protect against heart disease by reducing inflammation linked with HDL or good cholesterol.🍉Watermelon is around 90% water and also provides electrolytes such as potassium. This makes it a healthful choice of snack during the hot summer months.🍉The fiber and water content in watermelon may aid your digestive health by supporting regular bowel movements.🍉CAN DIABETIC EAT WATERMELON ?Watermelon is a fruit with natural sugar content. People with diabetes must account for these carbs in their daily meal plan. It is better to consume watermelon whole rather than as a juice as juicing removes the fiber making the sugar easier for the body to absorb. This may increase the risk of a glucose spike.🍉 Remember to watch portion sizes as with all fruit and juices."START ENJOY--TINGAND NOT DIETING"#intags #coach #weightlossblog #weightlossinspiration #beforeandafterweightloss #pcosweightloss #melon #DrinkWater #watermelonfresh #veganaf #intags #coach #weightlossblog #weightlossinspiration #beforeandafterweightloss #pcosweightloss #watermelon #melon #DrinkWater #watermelonfresh #veganaf #hotweather #summer #loveroffruit #missionaahar #eattolive #keepmoving #smile #onlinedietitian
comment:
{"1": {"comment_id": "missionaahar"  "comment_text": "BE YOUR OWN REASON TO SMILE.😄
The mandatory summer post. 🌞
🍉Red colour of this amazing summer fruit comes from lycopene  an antioxidant which protects from sun burn. Lycopene may help protect against heart disease by reducing inflammation linked with HDL or good cholesterol.
🍉Watermelon is around 90% water and also provides electrolytes  such as potassium. This makes it a healthful choice of snack during the hot summer months.
🍉The fiber and water content in watermelon may aid your digestive health by supporting regular bowel movements.

🍉CAN DIABETIC EAT WATERMELON ?
Watermelon is a fruit with natural sugar content. People with diabetes must account for these carbs in their daily meal plan. It is better to consume watermelon whole rather than as a juice  as juicing removes the fiber  making the sugar easier for the body to absorb. This may increase the risk of a glucose spike.
🍉 Remember to watch portion sizes as with all fruit and juices.

"START ENJOY--TING
AND NOT DIETING"

main_text: Mặt nạ ngủ chiết xuất từ dưa hấu của Glow Recipe🇺🇸Mặt nạ ngủ dưa hấu Watermelon Glow Sleeping Mask được lấy cảm hứng từ xu hướng da căng bóng đình đám xứ kim chi hứa hẹn mang đến cho người dùng làn da căng mọng mịn màng rạng rỡ nhờ 3 thành phần chính:tinh chất dưa hấu (cấp ẩm dưỡng da)Hyaluronic Acid (cấp ẩm)và AHA (tẩy da chết nhẹ nhàng trên bề mặt da).🇺🇸Với chất mask thơm nức đặc sánh nhưng không hề nhờn dính sản phẩm dùng được cho mọi loại da và được ví như một ly nước ép dưa hấu mát lành giúp giải khát cho làn da ngay tức thì. #glow #glowrecipe #watermelon #sleepingmask #skincare
comment:
{"1": {"comment_id": "lex_little_shop"  "comment_text": "Mặt nạ ngủ chiết xuất từ dưa hấu của Glow Recipe
🇺🇸Mặt nạ ngủ dưa hấu Watermelon Glow Sleeping Mask được lấy cảm hứng từ xu hướng da căng bóng đình đám xứ kim chi  hứa hẹn mang đến cho người dùng làn da căng mọng  mịn màng  rạng rỡ nhờ 3 thành phần chính:
tinh chất dưa hấu (cấp ẩm  dưỡng da) 
Hyaluronic Acid (cấp ẩm)
và AHA (tẩy da chết nhẹ nhàng trên bề mặt da).

🇺🇸Với chất mask thơm nức đặc sánh nhưng không hề nhờn dính  sản phẩm dùng được cho mọi loại da và được ví như một ly nước ép dưa hấu mát lành giúp giải khát cho làn da ngay tức thì. #glow #glowrecipe #watermelon #sleepingmask #skincare"}}

main_text: Listo el Lunch de las Morritas.¡Son Team Sandía como mamá! 🍉Hoy fue un día complicado para ser Mamá Godín... No siempre es así aveces pido un lunch de la cafetería que está justo enfrente de la escuela...
